{"tid":197107,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【選舉處失竊】再有細節曝光！職員冇將電腦鎖入櫃","createTime":"2017-04-11T16:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T12:32:30.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79ff94c8f8870695ebd0a49d6a5db37b2d903798","tid":197107,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處遺失全港逾370萬選民的個人資料，處方向立法會提交文件披露更多細節，包括處方3月24日把兩部載有選民資料的手提電腦留在選舉後備場地亞洲博覽館的上鎖房間後離開，直至3日後清場時才發現遺失電腦，該處承認兩部電腦只是存放在上鎖房間，並無放在上鎖的櫃內。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處的文件提到，該處職員於3月24日、即選舉前兩日，把兩部手提電腦帶到亞博館。其中一部載有378萬名地方選區選民的資料，包括每位選民的姓名、地址、身份證號碼、所屬選區、界別共5項資料；另一部電腦則載有在特首選舉有投票權的選委姓名。<br />\n<br />\n文件首次披露職員24日離開亞博館後，隨即通知亞博館控制中心將擺放手提電腦的門匙停用，改為上鎖模式，而有關電腦只是放在上鎖房間，並沒有鎖在櫃內。職員選舉結束後翌日上午10時到達亞博館清場，約兩小時後發現遺失電腦。<br />\n<br />\n總選舉事務主任黃思文早前曾承認載有全港選民的資料系統，不適宜應用於特首選舉，處方亦在文件表明，未來特首選舉使用的電腦，應只會儲存選委資料；該處又認為應在有需要啟用後備場地時，才把電腦運送到後備場地，而後備場地的保安安排應由主管級職員審批，並應向前線員工提供充足指示，但文件未有交代涉事職員會否受到處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170410/56547936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170410%2F56547936&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B80zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=90b8cc92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170410%2F56547936&h=d3c4ee42\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170410/56547936</a><br />\n<br />\n擺部腦喺度3日唔偷就笨柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f305a762b0e30f345ff19bafda660ef15350cf5","tid":197107,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561d8a1c6b14ddb789eafafeec6dd8af43234906","tid":197107,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處所有仆街死晒全家先再講"},{"pid":"97f5fb5998b29419d0fce76d546c1c697e03d5a4","tid":197107,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rw0j1uZLaig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drw0j1uZLaig&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B80zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=907a1394\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rw0j1uZLaig</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/ipooezok1/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fipooezok1%2Fimage.jpg&h=d0966159&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388b307fc5aec8fa08a1ff9300dacbc8cba8f4d5","tid":197107,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>選舉事務處所有仆街死晒全家先再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本公墓員就係仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n搵個弱智既去做都好過班仆街"},{"pid":"677971250871dc572ce705cb2d9642ffceab7f23","tid":197107,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"依家啲人已經唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a255aa79e4eb7df436eef2d65b6c894f047547a2","tid":197107,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"根本就突鳩登㗎啦佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4e5d2814300723760d0e6c4a46f5698e380d28","tid":197107,"uid":56245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694c9df84dda85376cf440ebfc53df63f8c91105","tid":197107,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}